      "description": "The frontend is a Next.js App Router project. The route tree covers the dashboard, sign-in, profile and organization pages, pull requests, issues, and settings. A components layer holds the UI building blocks, and a shared library layer provides client utilities along with the API proxy that talks to the backend.",
